Package: tipa
Title: Tau-independent phase analysis for circadian time-course data
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: as.person('Jake Hughey <jakejhughey@gmail.com> [aut, cre]')
Description: tipa accurately estimates phase shifts by accounting for period
  changes and for the point in the circadian cycle at which the stimulus occurs.
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
Imports:
	optimr (>= 2016-8.16)
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/hugheylab/tipa
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Suggests: 
  knitr,
  rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
BugReports: https://github.com/hugheylab/tipa/issues
